 "Pimp My Jokes: Interactive Standup Comedy in English Mondays at Süss War Gestern Wühlischstr 43 10245 Berlin  - zum Stadtplan Einschränkung: We kindly ask for a 10€ donation at the end of the show. Entry is free so you can leave if it's not making you happy. If you stay, pay Jeden Montag\n - Anfangszeit: 20:00 Uhr Kategorie: Comedy & Theater Standup comedy with 4 experienced comedians: Lineup show in the 1st half, brand new joke ideas workshopped as a panel with your input in the 2nd half. Pimp our jokes into bangers or watch them get dumped at the scrapyard. Either way, it's a hilarious ride with Berlin legends, rising stars and touring pros every Monday at Suess war gestern in English Doors 8:00pm Show 8:30pm Intermission 9:30 - 9:40pm Show end 10:30pm Entry: FREE Donation based show. Entry is free in the event you can't stay. We recommend a donation upwards of 10€ cash/card - if you stay, pay. YOUR HOST: ANNA BEROS (AUS) Anna’s a Kiwi born, Melbourne raised, Berlin based full-time standup comedian, writer and podcaster. Her solo shows Creampie Curious and Creampie Clarity had successful runs at the Edinburgh Fringe and Melbourne International Comedy Festival 2024. She also played Leicester Comedy Festival 2024 and in 2023 at Adelaide Fringe, Melbourne International Comedy Festival and Edinburgh Fringe. She tours Europe, has written for Comedy Central DE, hosts the YouTube channel Ersties Nonsense and has the podcast, Adults ONLY Comedy Berlin.She produces and hosts regular shows in Berlin including After Party Comedy, Back Door Comedy, Dirty Laundry Comedy, Top Shelf Comedy and this bad boiiii. IG @afberos LINEUP on IG stories @adultsonlycomedyberlin GUEST COMEDIANS: Local and touring comedians with solid years in the game or hard-working promising new blood who host regular shows and/or are performing solo von: AFB Mehr Infos im Internet: https://pimpmyjokes2025.eventbrite.co.uk Hinweis: AFB sucht nette Leute als Begleitung",
 'Kerzenwerkstatt / Candle workshop Weinmeisterstr. 15 10178 Berlin  - zum Stadtplan Einschränkung: Das Angebot findet während der Schulferien nicht statt. Nur mit Anmeldung. 8 bis 27 Jahre alt. 2€ pro Termin. Jeden Montag\n - Anfangszeit: 15:30 Uhr Kategorie: Kinder & Jugendliche In der upcycling Kerzenwerkstatt kannst du deine eigenen Kerzen ziehen, tauchen und verzieren. Du entscheidest die Größe deiner Kerze und kannst sie dann mit deinen eigenen Motiven, Düften, Verzierungen und Lieblingsfarben gestalten. Wenn du dein eigenes Gefäß mitbringst, kannst du auch eine Kerze pro Workshop selber gießen. Bring auch gerne Kerzenreste mit. Mo 15:30 – 17:00 Uhr | 8 bis 13 Jahre Mo 17:00 – 19:00 Uhr | 14 bis 27 Jahre 2€ Materialspende pro Termin Nur mit Anmeldung über Eventbrite:\xa0https://www.eventbrite.de/e/921379449737?aff=oddtdtcreator *Die Werkstatt findet an Feiertagen und während Schulferien nicht statt ----- In the Upcycling Candle Workshop, you can make your own candles by dipping, pulling, and decorating them. You decide the size of your candle and can then personalize it with your own designs, scents, decorations, and favorite colors. If you bring your own container, you can also pour a candle yourself during each workshop. Feel free to bring leftover candles as well. Mon 3:30 PM – 5:00 PM | 8 to 13 years Mon 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM | 14 to 27 years €2 material donation per session Eventbrite-Ticket required: https://www.eventbrite.de/e/921379449737?aff=oddtdtcreator. *The workshop does not take place on public holidays or during school vacations. von: WeinmeisterhausMitte Mehr Infos im Internet: https://weinmeisterhaus.de',
